OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FKey moments in the crushing
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof Afghan women's rights   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, "We are going to allow women to study  
OL,6, and work within our framework. Women   
OL,7, are going to be very active in our     
OL,8, society," the Taliban announced in     
OL,9, their first press conference shortly   
OL,10, after seizing power on 15 August 2021. 
OL,12,FTwo years on, these assurances have    
OL,13,Fbeen firmly demolished by the Taliban  
OL,14,Fgovernment's actions. The suppression  
OL,15,Fof women's rights under their rule is  
OL,16,Fthe harshest in the world, brought in  
OL,17,Fthrough a relentless series of         
OL,18,Freligious decrees from the Taliban     
OL,19,Fleadership, and regional rulings that  
OL,20,Fhave been steadily imposed across      
OL,21,FAfghanistan.                           
